These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, salsa
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, bus
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, russian
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the russian##3
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| Music-Genre    | salsa   | reggae        |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | rock-climbing |
| Transport     | bus  | motorbike       |
| Nationality     | spanish   | russian         |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta      |

