The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, romance
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, april
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, ivory
1. the tower house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| House         | tower   | townhouse |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | family     |
| Flower   | marigold  | bellflower        |
| Birthday           | august     | april       |
| Color         | green | ivory     |

